column5: Damn. sounds/looks like a great lake there you have, I need more days like that haha
Now that's a great way to spend a Tuesday!  Excellent report and some great fish!
looks like Dave is hooked, thanks for the report
Looks like you guys had a great time. I'm definitely in need of one of those getaways. Nice fish!
I have a fishing rod and can make myself free next Tuesday....

Thanks guys! - it really was a blast and Dave is already texting for the next time we can go lol he is in trouble now... soon the dreams will start! lol   I have a fishing rod and can make myself free next Tuesday....  lol - Schedule is different next week but thanks for your enthusiasm lol
A jewel of a spot there!!  Looks like a fantastic way to escape!  Thanks for the report.
Great report, looked like a blast. It's a great feeling bringing somebody out and watching them catch rush and have a blast! Awesome pics  Thanks for sharing!  MTBF
Great report , And a nice pike. R
Great report and nice catch. Dave is hooked now!!!
